---
title: Loaded Cheesy Lentil Nachos with Peppers and Salsa
description: This pub classic gets a veggie twist with tender spiced lentils and oodles of melty cheese! Served with sour cream and salsa, it's everyone's fav dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nachos-de-lentilles-au-fromage-0e8521b7.jpg
